{"tid":2011611,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(尋找香港最強) 煎釀三寶裡面既魚蛋","createTime":"2020-05-11T06:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T10:54:42.000Z","uid":224375,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c2bb64aacf83567b5caf2a2c5b82ba3347b975","tid":2011611,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"想知邊度比較好食<br />\n<br />\n我就以前土瓜灣天光道走鬼檔，唔係成日開，不過真心好食，裡面有洋蔥碎，好有咬口。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b2f7bf0c35b17db45ab4cf65519e54eca28161","tid":2011611,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣天光道走鬼檔？？<br />\n有冇廿年前"},{"pid":"99ef2665cc593944789fd1ac1a5b83deb85e7611","tid":2011611,"uid":224375,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"85b2f7bf0c35b17db45ab4cf65519e54eca28161","tid":2011611,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣天光道走鬼檔？？<br />\n有冇廿年前"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"差唔多，我一直記住，<br />\n因為實在太好食，<br />\n我一直都搵唔到有其他店比佢好食﹐勉強可以一鬥既話，係長洲夜晚近碼頭嗰檔走鬼檔<br />\n<br />\np.s 呢間天光道走鬼檔唔知有冇搬入舖頭"},{"pid":"afa056a1e961e00739b04718d924f5dd2a36a4c9","tid":2011611,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99ef2665cc593944789fd1ac1a5b83deb85e7611","tid":2011611,"uid":224375,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"85b2f7bf0c35b17db45ab4cf65519e54eca28161","tid":2011611,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣天光道走鬼檔？？<br />\n有冇廿年前"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"差唔多，我一直記住，<br />\n因為實在太好食，<br />\n我一直都搵唔到有其他店比佢好食﹐勉強可以一鬥既話，係長洲夜晚近碼頭嗰檔走鬼檔<br />\n<br />\np.s 呢間天光道走鬼檔唔知有冇搬入舖頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"到底係邊"},{"pid":"4e96d6bc01055905abe57afa4fcf084c10ba4ca6","tid":2011611,"uid":97089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c